{"word":"κομίζω","slug":"κομίζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ϰομίζω</el></b> [<el>ϰομέω</el> ‘take care of’]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘convey from a position’ and so <b>bring <a href='B:490 7:37'>Lk 7:37</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> most <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ freq.\">freq.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ mid.\">mid.</a> ‘be in receipt of’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> perspective of having received <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ someth.\">someth.</a> and then bringing it away <b>receive <a href='B:540 5:10'>2 Cor 5:10</a>; <a href='B:560 6:8'>Eph 6:8</a>; <a href='B:580 3:25'>Col 3:25</a></b> (sim<b>. <a href='B:680 2:13'>2 Pt 2:13</a></b>); <b><a href='B:650 10:36'>Hb 10:36</a>; <a href='B:650 11:39'>11:39</a>; <a href='B:670 1:9'>1 Pt 1:9</a>; <a href='B:670 5:4'>5:4</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp> get back <a href='B:470 25:27'>Mt 25:27</a>; <a href='B:650 11:19'>Hb 11:19</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:κομιεῖται\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:κομιοῦμαι\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}